Package: neonStageQplot
Type: Package
Title: Download and plot NEON hydrology data
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R: 
	c(person("Zachary", "Nickerson", email = "nickerson@battelleecology.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	  person("James", "Ross", email = "ross.james94@gmail.com", role=c("aut","ctb")),
	  person("Divine", "Aseaku", email = "divineaseaku@gmail.com", role=c("aut","ctb")))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <nickerson@battelleecology.org>
Description: Contains functions to download NEON Stage-discharge rating curves (DP4.00133.001), Continuous discharge (DP4.00130.001), Precipitation (DP1.00006.001), and Land-water interface images (DP1.20002.001) data products, summarize the data into 20 minute averages, and plot the data.
